condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section I. A. | Description :The borrower shall maintain, throughout Project Impt., the NSC on WRand NPMU, with an adequate composition, and ToRs satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :SemiAnnual

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section I. B. | Description :The Borrower shall adopt the Governance and Anti-Corruption Plan andensure the Project is carried out in accordance with the Plan. | Frequency :SemiAnnual
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section I. C. | Description :The Borrower shall adopt a Project Management Manual, in form andsubstance satisfactory to the Bank. | Due Date :22-Mar-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section I. D. a | Description :The Borrower shall issue a circular, in form and substancesatisfactory to the Bank, setting forth the procedures to be applied by the Participating Province or Kabupaten for the flow offunds, the role of the various parties, and the sanctions to be applied in the event of the use of funds for expenditures otherthan those required for the carrying out of the Project. | Due Date :14-Mar-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section I. D. b | Description :The Borrower shall enter into, and thereafter maintain in effectthroughout Project implementation, an on-granting agreement with the Participating Province or Kabupaten on terms and conditionsapproved by the Bank, specified in the Project Management Manual, incl. providing contributions as needed, and monitor and evaluatethe progress based on performance indicators | Due Date :14-Nov-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section I. F. | Description :The Borrower shall furnish to the Bank for approval no later thanSeptember 30 of each year, the annual work plan and budget for each subsequent year. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section I. G. | Description :The Borrower shall ensure that the Project is carried out in accordancewith the provisions of the Environmental and Social Safeguards Framework, the Environmental Management Plan etc. | Frequency:SemiAnnual

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section II. A.1 | Description :The Borrower shall monitor and evaluate the progress of the Projectand prepare semi-annual Project Reports on the basis of the agreed indicators. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section II. C(a) | Description :The Borrower shall carry out jointly with the Bank, no later than 30months after the Effective Date, a MTR to assess the status ofProject implementation. | Due Date :31-Oct-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section II. D. 2. | Description :The Borrower shall prepare and furnish to the Bank, interimunaudited financial reports for the Project covering the quarter, in form and substance satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency:Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2. Section II.D. 3 | Description :The Borrower shall have its Financial Statements audited byindependent auditors acceptable to the Bank in accordance with terms ofreference satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :Yearly
